		"Corina Păsăreanu"
	],
	"conference": "ICLR",
	"year": "2021",
	"date": "2021/01/01",
	"tldr": "This work contributes a post hoc robustness-certification algorithm that operates by efficienntly analyzing the linear regions of ReLU networks with *geometric projections* instead of expensive constraint solving, thus admitting an efficient, highly-parallel GPU implementation at the price of incompleteness, which can be addressed by falling back on prior approaches.",
